  "prompt": "Which are the best places to buy computer parts and accessories in Bangalore?",
  "response": "Bangalore is a hub for technology and electronics, offering numerous options for buying computer parts and accessories. Here are some of the best places to consider:\n\n1. **SP Road (Sadar Patrappa Road)**:\n   - Known as the go-to place for computer hardware and accessories.\n   - Offers a wide range of products from various brands at competitive prices.\n   - Shops are known for negotiating prices.\n\n2. **Brigade Road**:\n   - Popular shopping area with several electronics stores.\n   - You can find branded stores and smaller shops offering computer parts and accessories.\n\n3. **Indiranagar**:\n   - Has several specialized shops and retail chains like Croma and Reliance Digital.\n   - Good place for buying branded computer accessories and parts.\n\n4. **Koramangala**:\n   - Another area with many electronic and computer shops.\n   - Popular with tech enthusiasts and offers a variety of options.\n\n5. **Delta Peripherals**:\n   - Offers a wide range of computer components, accessories, and peripherals.\n   - Known for quality products and good customer service.\n\n6. **PC Shoppe**:\n   - Situated in the IT hub of Bangalore.\n   - Provides a comprehensive range of computer parts and accessories.\n\n7. **Genuine PC**:\n   - Specializes in genuine and high-quality computer parts.\n   - Known for reliable products and good customer support.\n\nWhen buying computer parts and accessories, it's essential to compare prices, check user reviews, and consider warranty and after-sales service. Moreover, verifying the authenticity of parts is crucial, especially if you are opting for lesser-known brands or refurbished items.",
